        <activityName xml:lang="en">sawnwood production, softwood, dried (u=20%), planed</activityName>
        <includedActivitiesStart xml:lang="en">Entry of the specific products issued of the planing activity</includedActivitiesStart>
        <includedActivitiesEnd xml:lang="en">Delivery of the generic planed product</includedActivitiesEnd>
        <generalComment>
          <text xml:lang="en" index="0">This activity is providing a more generic sawnwood product, combining inputs from the specific products issued from planing. The relative contribution is based on their Production Volumes.</text>
